data.description: Welcome to 146 Blackwater Way!  This great 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home is located within the sought after community of Fairmont South!  The first floor consists of a great office space, formal dining room, and cozy living room with a gas fireplace perfect for those chilly nights!  The open kitchen with eat in area features granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances including a gas range.  Upstairs you will find this floor plan provides an ample amount of space in each of the secondary bedrooms, bonus loft area, and generous sized laundry room.  The huge master suite is complete with double sinks in the bathroom, full size soaking tub, and walk in closet.  A fully fenced in private backyard can be enjoyed from the recently added screened in porch,or alternatively take in the breeze on the second story porch at the front of the home.  Conveniently located just minutes to shops and stores in Moncks Corner Marketplace.  Come take a look at all this great home and location have to offer!
